Package: ledgrcorespike
Type: Package
Title: Compiled Fold Core Measurement Spike For ledgr
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Max", "Thomasberger", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "max.thomasberger@gmail.com")
Description: Research spike measuring two compiled fold cores (Rust via
    extendr, C++ via cpp11) against post-v0.1.8.10 production R per
    ledgr's K1 horizon entry. Produces per-pulse and per-fill cost
    measurements with R callback boundary and inline static boundary
    variants. Not a production package; not intended for CRAN. May
    graduate to `ledgrcore` if the spike concludes "build authorized".
